Endagaano empya terina weragira oba okuwagira, nti Abakristaayo bagondere enkola ey'amateeka ag'ekimu eky'ekkumi.
Tewali ndagaano mpya wesalira muntu yenna muwendo gwalina kuwayo, wabula egamba ebirabo birina okuwebwaayo okusinziira ku nfuna y'omuntu (1 Abakolinso 16:2).
Amakanisa agamu gatwaala ebitundu ekkumi okuva mu ndagaano enkadde okuba omuwendo omuteme ogusembayo obutono abalokole gwebalina okuwaayo.
Endagaano empya eyogera ku mugaso ogw'okuwaayo eri Katonda.
Tulina okuwaayo ng'obusobozi bwaffe bwebuli.
Ebiseera ebimu kitegeeza okuwaayo okusukuluma ebitundu kkumi ku kikumi, era kitegeeza nti ebiseera ebimu mu busobozi bwaffe, tulina kuwayo ebitundu munana oba musanvu.
Okuwaayo kusinziira ku busobozi bw'omulokole, n'ebyetaago by'omubiri gwa Kristu.
Buli Mukristaayo alina okusaba Katonda amuluŋŋamye ku nsonga z'ebimu eby'ekkumi oba omuwendo ogw'okuwaayo (Yakobo1:5).
Okusingira ddala, ebimu eby'ekkumi n'ebiweebwayo byonna birina okuwebwayo n'ebigendererwa ebituufu era n'okwagala okusinza Katonda n'okuwereeza omubiri gwa Kristu.
