Omukkiriza tasobola kutuuka ku kigera kya bukulu mu mwoyo okujako nga afulumiza obuwereza, ate era ffena twetaaga okuyambibwa era okuzibwaamu amanyi abalunga abalala (1 Abakkolinso 12:21-26).
